ALIGN 4
Chapter1EscapeeList:
RequiredEscapee(Cleo)
RequiredEscapeeTerm

SetRequiredEscapeesList(Chapter1, Chapter1EscapeeList)

ALIGN 4
LoeweFinalEscapeQuoteList:
CharEscapeQuote(Chapter1,LoeweChapter1FinalEscapeQuoteText)
