CharEscapeQuote(Chapter9,LoeweChapter9EscapeQuoteText)
CharEscapeQuote(Chapter14,LoeweChapter14EscapeQuoteText)
CharEscapeQuote(Chapter16,LoeweChapter16EscapeQuoteText)
CharEscapeQuoteTerm


SetRequiredCharFinalEscapeQuoteList(Loewe, LoeweFinalEscapeQuoteList)

ALIGN 4
